These segments are used in flag rules for targeting:

| Segment Key | Name | Purpose |
|-------------|------|---------|
| `internal-orgs` | Internal Orgs | SailPoint internal testing orgs (matches by regex) |
| `staging-pods` | Staging Pods | All sandbox/staging pods across regions |
